\toc1 Jems Osirizir Ak…®nafarim 
\mt1 Jems Osirizir Ak…®nafarim 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 Jems 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Jems…®n ak…®nafarim akar aghuir av…®riba iti. Jems, God…®n gumazamiziba arazir aghuibar g…®n mangasa, a men sure damuasa akar aghuir av…®rir kaba osiri. A gumazamizibar akurvaght…® me n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ko fofozim iniva, egh derav…®ra an akam g…®n…®ghn…®ghasa an akar is…®n zuir av…®riba osiri. 
\ip Jems m…®gh…®ghav…®ra m…®g…®a ghaze, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itiba, me pura ikian kogham. Puvat…®. Me arazir aghuibar igharaz darazir amuam, eght…® arazir kam kamagh…®n akagham, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti. 
\c 1  
\ms1 E os…®mt…®zibar tuivigh gavgavigh egh derav…®ra God ko ikiam 
\mr (Sapta 1:1-18) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Matyu 13:55; Mak 6:3; Aposel 15:13; Galesia 1:19; 1 Pita 1:1\x*K…® Jems, k…® God ko Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n ingangarir gumazim. K…® ia 12plan Israel…®n itir anababa bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri. Kar ia gumazamizir uan nguibam ategha ghua kantrin igharazibar itiba. K…® dughiar aghuim ia gan…®di.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Israel…®n 12plan anabar kaba, da God…®n gumazamizir nguazir kam…®n bar an tibar ababanim gami.\f* 
\s1 Os…®mt…®ziba, da gavgavim e gan…®di 
\p  
\v 2-3 \x - \xo 1:2-3 \xt Aposel 5:41; Rom 5:3-5; Hibru 10:34; 1 Pita 1:6-7; 4:13; 4:16\x*Nan adarasi, ia fo, os…®mt…®zir ia bativiba, da ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibar amut…® ia tuivigh gavgavigh os…®mt…®ziba ater mang…®v…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ia bativt…®ma ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, ia bar akongegh.  
\v 4 Egh ia zurara tuivigh gavgavigh egh os…®mt…®ziba ater. Eght…® arazir kam ian ik…® gavgavigh mamagh…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n ia derav…®ra ik…®va, egh ia God…®n bizitam…®n oteveghan kogham. Puvat…®. Ian araziba bar deraght…®, ia God…®n Arazibar aghung mang…® gumazamizir aruabar m…®n otogham. 
\s1 Gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir aghuibar otevegh, me God ko m…®k…®m 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt 1 Atriviba 3:9-12; Aghuzir Akaba 2:3-6; Jon 15:7; 1 Jon 5:14-15\x*Ez…® ian tav n…®ghn…®zir aghuibar otevegh, a God…®n azangs…®ght…®ma, God a dan…®ngam. God pura biziba gumazamiziba bar me gan…®di, an atarir puvat…®. Kar God…®n bizibar anogorozir puvat…®zim, me an azangs…®zima a me dan…®ngasa bar ifonge.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Mak 11:24; 1 Timoti 2:8\x*Eght…® n…® God ko m…®k…®m…®va, n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®, n…®ghn…®zir pumuning ikian mark…®, egh suam, ‚ÄúGod ti bizitam na danigham, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù E fo, gumazim o amizim n…®ghn…®zir pumuning iti, a mati am…®nim ongarim givav amadima a pura tintinibar d…®kafi.  
\v 7 A kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, Ekiam bizitam a danigham. Puvat…®.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Jems 4:8\x*A okam n…®ghn…®gha, n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami, arazir an amiba, da n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ran itir puvat…®. 
\s1 Jems onganaraziba ko gumazir bizir av…®riba itiba akam me gan…®di 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Jems 2:5\x*Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itir gumazamiziba, onganarazibagh amua iti, me God…®n damazim…®n ziar ekiam iti. Kamagh…®n, me bar akuegh ik…®.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Korin 7:31; 1 Jon 2:17\x*Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itir gumazamiziba, bizir av…®riba iti, me fo, God g…®n me d…®kab…®raght…® me ak…®marir atiabar m…®n aremegham. Kamagh…®n, me uaghan bar akuegh ik…®.  
\v 11 E fo, aruem anaga pamtem gara temem gisiraz…®ma a m…®d…®i. Ez…® temem…®n ak…®marir aghuiba suaghira, egha dar ganganim bar ikufi. Ez…® kamagh…®ra gumazamizir bizir av…®riba itiba, me uan ingangarim damuv…®ra ik…®va an tong…®n aremegham. 
\s1 God arazir aghuibar e gami, egha arazir kurabar amuasa e ab…®rir puvat…® 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 3:11-12; 2 Timoti 4:8; Hibru 12:5; Jems 2:5; 1 Pita 5:4; Akar Mogomem 2:10\x*Gumazim os…®mt…®ziba ater…®va, egh uaghan os…®mt…®ziba bar dar aven tugh gavgavigh, uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ateghan koght…®, God ivezir aghuim a dan…®ngt…®ma a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim iniam. Ivezir aghuir kam, God akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua ghaze, gumazir bar a gifongeziba, a me dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n, gumazir kam bar akongegh. 
\p  
\v 13 Kamagh…®n gumazitam bizitam an navim ab…®raght…®ma an arazir kuratam damigham, a kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, ‚ÄúGod na ab…®raz…®ma k…® arazir kam gami.‚Äù Puvat…®. E fo, gumazitam God ab…®raght…®ma an arazir kuratam damighan kogham, eght…® God gumazitam ab…®raght…®ma an arazir kuratam damighan kogham.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Rom 7:7-10\x*Ez…® en navir kuraba vaghvagha arazir kurabar amuasa e gifarava e apezeperava e gakaghori.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Onger Akaba 7:14; Rom 5:19-21\x*Ez…® navir d…®gavir kam, a mati amizim navim adai, egha g…®n arazir kuram gamiz…®ma an oto, mati a borim…®n bate. Ez…® arazir kuram ghua ekevezir dughiam, an ovevem gamiz…®ma an oto.  
\v 16 Nan adarasi, ia gumazitam ateght…® a ia gifaran mark…®.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Malakai 3:6; Matyu 7:11; Jon 3:27; Rom 11:29; 1 Korin 4:7\x*Bizir bar aghuir e isiba, ko bizir ikuvir puvat…®ziba, da bar God…®n Nguibam…®n p…®n izaghiri. God Afeziam a biziba bar overiam dar ingari, a bizir aghuir kaba e bagha da amadi da izaghiri. Ez…® Afeziar kam a uan araziba ragh…®razir puvat…®. A bizitam…®n nedazim…®n m…®n aruem a gisiraz…® an otevegha ruarazir puvat…®. A kamagh…®ra iti.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Jon 1:13; Efesus 1:12; 1 Pita 1:23; Akar Mogomem 14:4\x*God kamaghsua, a biziba bar dar ingari, egha e gamiz…® e bar adar faragh mangam. Kamagh…®n God uab…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghuava en Afeziam…®n oto, a uan guiz…®n akam…®n e gamiz…®ma e otifi. 
\ms1 E n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim guizbang…®ra God…®n ik…®, e uaghan arazir aghuibar amuam 
\mr (Sapta 1:19--5:6) 
\s1 E God…®n Akam baragh, uaghan an g…®n mangam 
\p  
\v 19 Nan adarasi, ia derav…®ra bizir kam g…®fogh. Ia bar zuam…®ra kuaribar ar…®gh akaba baragh, egh zuam…®ra m…®k…®man mark…®, egh zuam…®ra ataran mark…®.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 10:19; 17:27; Fofozir Gumazim 5:1-2; 7:9\x*E fo, atarir gumazim, God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh amima da otivir puvat…®.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt 1 Korin 15:2; Kolosi 3:8; Hibru 2:3; 1 Pita 1:9; 2:1\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bar arazir m…®z…®r…®ziba ko arazir kurar otiviba, ia bar ada munamadagh. Egh ia bar uari d…®kab…®ragh egh Akar God ian navir averiam…®n d…®karazim inigh. Eght…® Akar kam ian akuragham.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Matyu 7:21; 7:26; Luk 6:46; Rom 2:13; 1 Jon 3:7\x*Egh Akar ia inizir kam, ia an m…®rara mang…®. Ia puram orarazir k…®nim damuan mark…®. Puvat…®. Ia pura orarazir k…®nim…®n damuam, kamagh…®n ia uarira uarigh ifari.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Luk 6:47; Jems 2:14\x*Gumazamiziba pura God…®n Akam baregha, an g…®n zuir puvat…®, me mati gumazamiziba ganganim…®n uan guabar gari.  
\v 24 Egha me derav…®ra uan guabar ganigha, ua ghugha ok…®n…®ghn…®ki, men guaba manmagh…®ra gari.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Jon 13:17; Rom 8:2; 2 Korin 3:18; Jems 2:12\x*Ez…® God…®n Akar bar derav…®ra itim e gamima e f…®riagh…®r…®. Eght…® gumazamiziba derav…®ra Akar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, egh pura Akam baragh zuam…®ra ok…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogh, bar an Akam…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, gumazamizir kaba, God men ingangaribar amut…® da bar derav…®ram otivam. 
\p  
\v 26 \x - \xo 1:26 \xt Onger Akaba 34:13; 39:1; 141:3; 1 Pita 3:10\x*Gumazamizitaba kamagh…®n n…®ghnigh suam, ‚ÄúE God…®n gumazamizir bar aghuiba, egha guizbang…®ra an ziam fe,‚Äù egha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuibar uan m…®zebar dav geir puvat…®, kamagh…®n me uarira uarigh ifari. Ez…® kamagh…®n men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ko God…®n ziam fer arazim pura bizim.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt Aisaia 1:16-17; 58:6-7; Rom 12:2\x*Guizbang…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir God Afeziam…®n damazim…®n deragha os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®zim, a kamak…®n: E borir ameboghfeziaba ovengezibar akurvagh…®va, amizir odiarir men paba ovengeziba sarama akurvagh, men os…®mt…®ziba ateram. Ez…® uaghan bizir mam, e uari uan daroriba derav…®ra dar ganam, eght…® nguazir kam…®n araziba e damut…® e God…®n damazim…®n m…®zeghan kogham. 
\c 2  
\s1 E arazir amir vam…®ran, bar gumazamizibar amuam 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt God…®n Araziba 1:17; Aghuzir Akaba 24:23; Matyu 22:16; Aposel 10:34; Jems 2:9\x*Nan adarasi, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim en Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n iti, a bizir aghuir God…®n Nguibam…®n itibar Ekiam. Ia gumazamizir ziaba itiba derav…®ra me damu egh gumazamizir ziaba puvat…®ziba ak…®rim ragh me gasan mark…®. Ia amir arazir vam…®ran bar me damu.  
\v 2 Eght…® gumazitam kurukazir bar aghuim damigh, egh gol…®n ring uan dafarim dat…®gh, God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven mangam, eght…® gumazir onganarazim korotiar b…®b…®zibar kurukegh egh uaghan God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven mangam,  
\v 3 eght…® kurukazir bar aghuim gamizir gumazim ia derav…®ra a damuva, egh a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúAruam, n…® iz…® dabirabir aghuir kam daperagh,‚Äù egh ia onganarazibagh amir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúN…® munagh tugh,‚Äù o ‚ÄúN…® nan dagarimning borogh…®n magh vazim daperagh,‚Äù  
\v 4 Ian arazir kam mati, ia uan n…®ghn…®zibar aven igharaz darazi ab…®gha men araziba tuis…®si. Egha ia derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gha gumazamizibar araziba arazir vam…®ran me tuis…®zir pu. Puvat…®. Ia mati jasbar m…®n otivigha n…®ghn…®zir bar kurabar gumazamiziba tuis…®si. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Matyu 5:3; Jon 7:48; 1 Korin 1:26-28; 1 Timoti 6:18\x*Nan adarasi, ia oragh. Nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibar damazibar itir gumazamizir onganaraziba, gumazamizir kaba God me am…®sevegha ghaze, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n arazim…®n iti. A fom…®ra gumazamizir bar a gifongeziba bagha akam ak…®ra ghaze, a bar me gativagh men ganam. Kamagh…®n a gumazamizir onganarazir kaba m…®sevegha ghaze, me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ikiam.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Aposel 13:50; 18:12; 1 Korin 11:22\x*Ez…® ia akar aghums…®ziba onganarazibagh an…®di. Ia n…®ghn…®gh! Tina ia d…®kab…®ra egha os…®mt…®ziba ia gar…®si, egha ia m…®k…®rvagha kotiabar zui? Kar gumazamizir dag…®aba bar iz…®vaziba arazir kabagh ami.  
\v 7 Ez…® God Iesus…®n ziar aghuim ia gat…®, ez…® tina ziar aghuir kam gas…®ghas…®si? Dag…®ar av…®riba itir gumazamizir kabara. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Ofa Gami 19:18; Matyu 19:19; 22:39; Rom 13:8-9; Galesia 5:14\x*God en atrivir ekiam, egha an Ak…®nafarim…®n an akar ekiar mam e gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uab…®ra uab…® gifongez…® mogh…®n, gumazamizir igharazibagh ifongegh.‚Äù Egh ia akar kam guizbang…®ra a baragh an g…®n mang…®, kamagh…®n ia arazir aghuim damuam.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt God…®n Araziba 1:17\x*Ez…® ia arazir aghuim gumazamizir mabagh amua egha gumazamizir igharaziba ak…®rim me gasara, kamagh…®n ia arazir kuram gami. Ez…® Moses Osirizir Araziba kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ia an akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt God…®n Araziba 27:26; Matyu 5:19; Galesia 3:10\x*Eght…® ian tina Moses Osirizir Araziba bar dar g…®n mang…®va, egh arazir vam…®ra abigh…®va, kamagh…®n an arazir kuram gami. A mati gumazim o amizir Moses Osirizir Araziba bar da b…®ghizim.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:13-14; God…®n Araziba 5:17-18; Rom 13:9\x*E fo, God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim damuan mark…®.‚Äù Egha a uaghan kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazamizibav soght…®ma me ar…®m…®ghiran mark…®.‚Äù Eght…® ia poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim damuan kogh…®va, egh ia gumazitam m…®sueght…® an aremegham, kamagh…®n ia Moses Osirizir Araziba ab…®zir gumazamizibar otifi. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Galesia 6:2; Jems 1:25-26; 1 Pita 2:16\x*Ia fo, God…®n Arazim en arazir kuram…®n gavgavim a g…®vagham, egh…®va e damut…® e f…®righ…®r…®gham. Egh g…®n God uan arazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®va egh en araziba tuis…®gham. Kamagh…®n, ia gumazamizir God…®n Arazim…®n apengan itibar akaba ko araziba zurara dar amu.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 21:13; Matyu 5:7; 18:32-35; 25:41-42\x*E fo, gumazamiziba igharaz darazir apangkuvan koght…®, God kotiam…®n me tuis…®ghamin dughiam…®n, God uaghan men apangkuvighan kogham. Ez…® gumazim o amizim igharaz darazir apangkufi, God kotiam…®n a tuis…®ghamin dughiam…®n a God…®n apangkuvim…®n ganam. 
\s1 N…®ghn…®zir gavgavim arazir aghuim sara zuir puvat…®, a pura bizim 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Matyu 7:21; 7:26; Jems 1:23\x*Nan adarasi, gumazitam o amizitam suam, ‚ÄúK…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n iti,‚Äù egha an arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®, kamagh…®n an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim pura bizim. An n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam ti an akuragham, o puvat…®gham? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Jop 31:19-20; Luk 3:11; 1 Jon 3:17\x*Ez…® Krais…®n adarazir aveghbuatam o buaramizitam, korotiaba ko dagheba puvat…®,  
\v 16 eght…® ian tav kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúN…® navir am…®rizim…®n ik…®. N…® mang…®va inim ikegh…®va uan m…®karzim avaragh. Egh mang…® dagher av…®ribar am…®va egh navim iz…®fagh.‚Äù Eght…® akar kam manmagh…®n an akuragham? Ia uari korotiaba ko dagheba an akurvaght…®ma a derav…®ra ikiam.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Jems 2:20; 2:26\x*Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n arazim uaghan kamagh…®ra ghu. N…®ghn…®zir gavgavim pura ikia, egha arazir aghuiba sara zuir puvat…®, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam, an aremez…® mogh…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 2:18 \xt Galesia 5:6; Jems 3:13\x*Tav kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúGumazamizir maba n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba iti, ez…® gumazamizir igharaziba arazir aghuibagh ami.‚Äù K…® kamagh…®n n…®n akam ikaragham, ‚ÄúN…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia egha arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®, kamagh…®n k…® manmagh…®n n…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim g…®fogham? K…® arazir aghuibar amuam, eght…® arazir kabara nan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…®n akagham.‚Äù  
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Matyu 8:29; Luk 4:34; Aposel 16:17\x*N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n ikia ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n vam…®ra iti.‚Äù A dera. Duar kuraba uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam ikia, egha agoa atiati. 
\p  
\v 20 N…® gumazamizir onganiba! Ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavimra ikiava egha arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®, kamagh…®n ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim a pura bizim. Ia ti akar kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghasa, o? Ia oragh.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Jenesis 22:1-14\x*Fom…®ra en ovavim Abraham uan otarim Aisak isa ofa gamir dakozim…®n anet…®gha God…®n ofa gami mogh…®n a gami. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n God an arazim…®n ganigha egha Abraham m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® nan damazim…®n dera.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Hibru 11:17-18\x*Ia bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Abraham…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ko an arazir aghuim vorogh…®ra ghu. Ez…® arazir aghuir kam bar an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gamima a guizbang…®ra gavgafi.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Jenesis 15:6; 2 Eghaghaniba 20:7; Aisaia 41:8; Rom 4:3; 4:9; 4:22; Galesia 3:6\x*God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAbraham n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itima, God an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim bagha a d…®bora ghaze, n…® nan damazim…®n dera.‚Äù Egha God kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúNan roroam.‚Äù Ez…® akar kam…®n m…®ngarim, God a gamiz…®ma me Ak…®nafarim…®n an osiri, Abraham uan otarim Aisak gamizir dughiam…®n arazir kam, a bar azenan oto.  
\v 24 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia fo, gumazitam pura n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, God, ‚Äúgumazir God…®n damazim…®n derazim,‚Äù a d…®borir pu. Bar puvat…®. A gumazir arazir aghuim gamim g…®n…®ghn…®gha, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavimra g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, egha bizir kam bagha God a d…®bora ghaze, a nan damazim…®n dera. 
\p  
\v 25 \x - \xo 2:25 \xt Josua 2:1-21; Hibru 11:31\x*Ez…® tuavir kamra, arazir kurabagh amir amizim Rahap, moga garir gumazir Josua amadazimning…®n akuragha aning amadaz…®ma aning tuavir igharazim…®n ghu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma God amizir kam m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® nan damazim…®n dera.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 2:26 \xt Jems 2:17\x*E fo, gumazim…®n m…®karzim duam an aven itir puvat…®, an aremegha g…®fa. Kamagh…®ra, gumazim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia, egha arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®, gumazir kam…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim aremez…® mogh…®n iti. 
\c 3  
\s1 E uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba derav…®ra dar ganam 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Matyu 23:8; 23:14; Luk 6:37; 12:47; 1 Pita 5:3\x*Nan adarasi, God gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®ghamin dughiam…®n, e gumazamizir, gumazamizibar sure gamir ingangarim iniziba, God bar derav…®ra en ingangariba tuis…®gham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ian tarazira God ifongezir arazibar gumazamizibar sure damuamin ingangarim inighan kogham.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt 1 Atriviba 8:46; Aghuzir Akaba 20:9; Matyu 12:37; 1 Jon 1:8\x*Dughiar av…®ribar e bizir vabara damuasa n…®ghn…®gha, paza dagh ami. Bizir kaba bar e batifi. Eght…® gumazitam dughiatam…®n paz…® m…®kemeghan kogh, a bar gumazir aghuimra, egh a uan m…®karzim bar derav…®ram a geghuv an gan. 
\p  
\v 3 E ain…®n oteviba isa hoziabar akabar aright…®, ain…®n otevir kaba dar amut…® da en akaba baragh…®va derav…®ra mangam. Ez…® arazir kam…®n e bar derav…®ra dar gant…®, da en g…®n mangam.  
\v 4 Ez…® ia kuribagh n…®ghn…®gh. Kuriba bizir bar ekiaba, ez…® am…®nir ekiar gavgaviba dagh ivaima, da ongarim gis…®n ivemari. Ez…® dar stiaba bar sufi. Ez…® dar stian suizir gumaziba managh mangasa ifongegha, dar stiaba g…®ghavk…®rima kuriba tuavir keptenba mangasa ifongezibar zui.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Onger Akaba 12:3; 73:8-9; Aghuzir Akaba 12:18; 15:2\x*Ez…® kamagh…®ra, m…®zem uaghan bar suvigha en m…®karzim…®n aven iti. Egha a zurara bar puv…®ra ifaghata, uab…® uan ziam puv a fe. E fo, avir muziarimra avir ekiam damight…® a bar ekeveght…®, ruarim…®n temeba bar isigham!  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 16:27; Matyu 12:36-37; 15:11; 15:18-19; Mak 7:15; 7:20; 7:23\x*Ez…® m…®zem uaghan mati avim, egha a en m…®karzir otevir muziarir mam. Egha a uaghan arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami da otifi. A en m…®karzibagh amima da m…®ze, egha arazir kurar av…®ribagh amima da en ik…®r…®m…®ribar otifi, mati avir m…®zariar ekiaba. Avir kam a uab…® hel…®n avim. 
\p  
\v 7 E fo, gumazamiziba as…®zir atiaba bar mogh…®ra da isava dar dai, kuaraziba ko as…®zir davaragharuiba ko ongarim…®n aven itir biziba bar. Egha me bizir kabar dava dar gari da men apengan iti.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Onger Akaba 140:3; Rom 3:13\x*Gumazitam o amizitam uab…® uan m…®zem damight…® an an apengan ikeghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. En m…®zeba zurara akar kurabav gei. Mati imezir kurar gumazamizibagh ami me ariagh…®riba, da en akabagh iz…®fa. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Jenesis 1:26; 1 Korin 11:7\x*E uan m…®zebar Ekiam…®n ziam fe, a en Afeziam. God gumazamizibar ingariz…®ma me an m…®rara otifi, ez…® e uan m…®zebar e akar kurabav g…®ava gumazamizir igharazibagh as…®ghas…®si.  
\v 10 Ekiam fer akaba ko akar kuraba, aning v…®rara m…®zer vam…®ram otifi. Nan adarasi, arazir kam a ikian kogham.  
\v 11 Mozir d…®patam, d…®par aghuim ko ongarir pam, uaning veregh ikiam ti? Puvat…®!  
\v 12 Nan adarasi, figh…®n temem oliv…®n temem…®n m…®n bam, o? Puvat…®! O wain…®n ikar…®zim a figh…®n temem m…®n bam, o? Puvat…®! Kamagh…®ra d…®par apir aghuim ongarir d…®pam ko ik…®va otivan kogham. 
\s1 Gumazamiziba God…®n izezir fofozim ik…®va, me arazir aghuibar amuam 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Galesia 6:4; Jems 1:21; 2:18\x*Ez…® tinara ian tong…®n fofozir aghuim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuim iti, o? Kamagh…®n amir gumazitam o amizitam ik…®va, an dabirabim bar deragham. A fofozir aghuim…®n arazibar g…®n mang…®va gumazamizibar asughasugh…®va egh uab…® uan ziam fan kogham. Eght…® gumazamiziba an arazir aghuir an amibar ganam.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Rom 2:17; 2:23; 13:13\x*Eght…® ia igharaz darazi navir bar kuraba men ik…®va, egh zurara uan ziaba f…®s…® tuaviba buriam, kamagh…®n ia uan fofozim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba bagh bar akueghan mark…®. Ia ifaragh uan arazibar guiz…®n akam d…®kab…®raghan mark…®.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Filipai 3:19; Jems 1:5; 1:17\x*Ez…® fofozir kam a God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegha izir pu. Puvat…®, kar nguazir kam…®n bizim. A navir ghurim…®n oto. Ez…® Satan, an afeziam.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Korin 3:3\x*Ia oragh. Gumazamiziba navir kuraba gumazamizir igharazibar iti, egha me zurara uan ziaba fasa tuaviba buri, gumazamizir kaba me navir vam…®ra itir puvat…®. Me arazir bar kurar av…®ribagh ami. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Rom 12:9; 1 Korin 2:6-7; 1 Pita 1:22; 1 Jon 3:18\x*Ez…® gumazamizir fofozir aghuir God…®n Nguibam…®n izezim iniziba, me arazir kabagh ami: Faragha zuir arazim, me zurara n…®ghn…®zir zuezibar g…®n zui. Egha me igharaz darazi ko navir vam…®ran iti, egha gumazamizibar asughasusi. Egha me gumazamizir igharazibar akaba barasi. Me igharaz darazir apangkuva egha arazir aghuibar me gami. Egha me arazir kamra gumazamiziba bar me gami. Egha me arazir aghuibar g…®n ghua ifarir puvat…®. Me bar guizbang…®ra dar g…®n zui.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 11:18; Aisaia 32:17; Matyu 5:9; Filipai 1:11; Hibru 12:11\x*Ez…® kamagh…®n e navir vam…®ra iti, kar mati e dagher anabam akara. Ez…® navir vam…®ran arazim…®n tuavim…®n, arazir aghuiba en dabirabim…®n otifi, mati dagher aghuiba azenim…®n aghui. 
\c 4  
\s1 Gumazamizir nguazim…®n arazibagh ifongeziba, me God…®n apaniba 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Rom 7:23; Galesia 5:17; 1 Pita 2:11\x*Bizir m…®ngarir manaba adariba ko m…®dorozibagh amima da ian tong…®n otifi? M…®karzim…®n agorogem…®n araziba ian navibar iti, egha da ian m…®karzibar aven ikia ia ko m…®sosi, kamagh…®n amiz…®, arazir kam…®n da akamadariba ko m…®dorozibagh amima da otifi. Kamagh…®n ti puvat…®, o?  
\v 2 Ia biziba iniasa bar ifonge, egha ia da isir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia gumazamizibav sozi me ariaghiri. Ia biziba iniasa dagh agoa, egha ia da isir puvat…®. Egha ia puv atara m…®sosi. Ia biziba iniasa God ko m…®geir puvat…®, ez…® bizir kam bagha ia da isir puvat…®.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt Onger Akaba 66:18; Aisaia 1:15; Maika 3:4; Sekaraia 7:13; 1 Jon 3:22\x*Egha ia biziba iniasa God ko m…®g…®a, egha da isir puvat…®. Ian n…®ghn…®ziba derazir puvat…®z…®ma ia God ko m…®gei. Ia bizir ian m…®karzim…®n agorogem itiba bagha n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n, ia biziba isir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Jon 15:19; 17:14; Rom 8:7; 1 Jon 2:15\x*Ia God ataki, mati amizim uan pam ategha ghua gumazir igharaziba isava akui. Ia orakigh! Ian tav nguazim…®n arazibagh ifonge, a God…®n apanim. Ez…® ia ti bizir kam g…®fozir puvat…®, o? Gumazim o amizim nguazim…®n arazibar namakam gami, a God…®n apanim…®n oto.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:3-5; D…®boboniba 11:29\x*God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDuar God en navir averiabagh at…®zir kam, e God uab…®n apengara ikiasa a bar ifonge.‚Äù Ia ti ghaze, akar kam ti pura bizim? Puvat…®.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Onger Akaba 138:6; Aghuzir Akaba 3:34; Luk 14:11; 1 Pita 5:5\x*God en apangkuvav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúGod zurara gumazir uan ziaba feba a me d…®kab…®ri, 
\q2 egha gumazir uan ziaba d…®kab…®riba 
\q3 God men apangkuva 
\q4 egha bar derav…®ra me gami.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Efesus 4:27; 6:11-12\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uari d…®kab…®ragh egh God…®n apengan ik…®. Ia Satan munasaraght…®, a ia ategh ar…®mang…®gham.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 15:2; Aisaia 1:16; Sekaraia 1:3; Malakai 3:7; Jems 1:8; 1 Jon 3:3\x*Ia God…®n borogh…®ra mang…®t…®, a ian borogh…®ra izam. Ia arazir kurabagh amir gumazamiziba, ia uan navir averiabar amight…® da zuegh, mati gumazamiziba uan dafariba ruez…® da bar zue. Ez…® ia gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir pumuning itiba, n…®ghn…®zir kurar ian navibar itiba, ia da atakigh.  
\v 9 Ia naviba bar osemegh egh pamtem arang…®va aziam. Ia gumazamizir dat…®r…®gh…®n atiba, ia uan akazim ategh, egh ia arang. Ia gumazamizir bar akongeziba, ia uan agoroger kam ategh, naviba bar osemegh azi ik…®.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Jop 5:11; 22:29; Matyu 23:12; 1 Pita 5:6\x*Ia God…®n damazim…®n bar uari d…®kab…®ragh ik…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, God ia fegham. 
\s1 E akaba igharaz darazigh asan kogham 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Luk 6:37; Rom 2:1; Efesus 4:31; 1 Pita 2:1\x*Nan adarasi, ia God…®n gumazamizir igharaziba akar kurabar me m…®k…®man mark…®. Ian tina akar kuram…®n igharazitav m…®keme, o akam a gasi, an akar kuram…®n Moses Osirizir Arazibav gei, egha a Moses Osirizir Araziba iria. Ez…® ia Moses Osirizir Araziba iria, ia mati gumazim o amizim Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan itir pu. Puvat…®. Ia jas…®n m…®n oto.\f + \fr 4:11 \ft Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven itir akar otevir kam, Jems ti vez…®n kam…®n a gin…®r…®. Kar akar Ofa Gami 19:18 ko Jems 2:8…®n itim.\f* 
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Matyu 10:28; Rom 2:1; 14:4; 14:13\x*God uab…®ra Moses Osirizir Araziba an…®di, egha a uab…®ra jas. A uab…®ra gumazamizibar akurvagham, o me gas…®ghas…®gham. Kamagh…®n ia te, ia jas…®n m…®n gumazamizir igharaziba tuis…®si? 
\s1 E kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, Ekiam ifueght…®ma, e bizir e n…®ghn…®zibar amuam 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Luk 12:18-20\x*\x - \xo 4:13-14 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 27:1\x*Ia oragh, ian tina suam, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n, o gurumzaraghan e nguibar ekiar mam…®n mang…®gh…®va dag…®ar ingangarim azenir vam…®ran a damigham. Egh arazir kam…®n e dag…®ar av…®riba iniam.‚Äù  
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Onger Akaba 39:5; 39:11; 102:3; Jems 1:10; 1 Pita 1:24\x*Ia zurara kamagh…®n m…®g…®a, egha ia fozir puvat…®, bizir manam gurumzaraghan otivam. Ian ik…®r…®m…®rim mati m…®gharim, a dughiar otevimra ikegh…®va bar g…®vagham.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 4:15 \xt Aposel 18:21; 1 Korin 4:19; Hibru 6:3\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®m, ‚ÄúEkiam ifueght…®ma, e angam…®ra ik…®va, bizir e n…®ghn…®zibar amuam.‚Äù  
\v 16 Ez…® ian arazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n amim, ia uari uan ziaba fava egha ingangarir ekiabar amuasa dar gun m…®gei. Ia uari fer akar kam, a bar ikufi.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Luk 12:47; Jon 9:41; 15:22; Rom 1:20-21; 2:17-18; 2:23\x*Ia derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gh! Ia arazir aghuir damuamin tam g…®fogh, egh ia a damuan kogh, kamagh…®n ia arazir kuram gami. 
\c 5  
\s1 Gumazamizir bizir av…®riba itiba me ivezir kuram iniam 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 11:28; Luk 6:24; 1 Timoti 6:9\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, bizir av…®riba itir gumazamiziba, k…® akam ia m…®k…®masa ifonge. Ia oragh! Ia os…®mt…®zir ekiar ia bativamibagh n…®ghnigh, pamtem d…®m…®va arang ik…®.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Jop 13:28\x*\x - \xo 5:2-3 \xt Matyu 6:19\x*Ian bizir aghuiba da bar ikuvigham. Eght…® ian korotiaba barareba dar ghoregham.  
\v 3 Eght…® ian gol ko silvaba bar m…®ghovegham, eght…® m…®z…®r…®zir kam ian arazir kurabar amight…® da azenim giregham. Eght…® m…®z…®r…®zir kam avim…®n m…®n ian m…®karzibar isiam. Ekiam izamin dughiam bar rogh…®ra izi, ez…® ia pura biziba ko dag…®aba akuvaz…®ma da iti.\f + \fr 5:3 \ft God gumazamizibar arazibar tuis…®ghamin dughiam…®n, a dag…®ar av…®riba itir gumazibar bizir aghuibar gan…®va da tuis…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®. A men arazibar gan…®va da tuis…®gham. Gumazir kaba, bizir bar ikuvigham dar suiki, ez…® bizir kam en aka ghaze, me nguazim…®n itir dughiam…®n me arazir aghuim gamir puvat…®. Ez…® avir kam…®n akam ghaze, me ivezir kuram iniam.\f* 
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt God…®n Araziba 24:14-15; Jeremaia 22:13; Malakai 3:5\x*Ia derav…®ra oragh, ingangarir gumazamiziba ian azenibar dagheba isi, ez…® ia me gifaragha men ivezir mabar anogoroke. Ez…® ingangarir gumazamizir kaba me uan ivezibagh n…®ghn…®gha, God…®n d…®a ghaze, a ian arazir kuraba ikarvagham. Ez…® ingangarir gumazamizibar d…®mdiam, Ekiar Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a baraki.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Jeremaia 12:3; 25:34; Amos 6:1; 6:4; Luk 16:19; 16:25; 1 Timoti 5:6\x*Ez…® dughiar ia nguazir kam…®n itim, ia bizir aghuir av…®riba isa bar akuegha iti. Egha ia dagher av…®riba apa bar ekefe. Ez…® God ia m…®soght…® ia ar…®m…®ghiramin dughiam, an otogha g…®fa.  
\v 6 Ia gumazamizir aghuibar kotim gamigha me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® me ian gavgavim munamadir puvat…®gha, ia ikarvagha ia m…®soghezir puvat…®. 
\ms1 Ia gavgavigh ik…®va God ko m…®k…®m, egh Ekiam m…®zuamt…®  // a ua izam 
\mr (Sapta 5:7-20) 
\s1 E gavgavigh ik…®va os…®mt…®ziba ater…®va egha Ekiam m…®zuamt…® a izam 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 5:7 \xt God…®n Araziba 11:14; Jeremaia 5:24; Hosea 6:3; Joel 2:23; Sekaraia 10:1; Luk 21:19\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, nan adarasi, ia tuivigh gavgavigh os…®mt…®ziba ater…®va Ekiam m…®zuamt…® a ua izam. Ia fo, gumazim o amizir azenim itim, a dagher aghuiba an azenim…®n aghungasa an adav zuai. Egha a gavgavim uan navim gan…®ga aghumra ikiava amozim ko aruem m…®zuai, aning uan ingangarim faragh a damuam. Eght…® a g…®n dagheba iniam.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Rom 13:11-12; Filipai 4:5; Hibru 10:25; 10:37; 1 Pita 4:7\x*Ez…® ia uaghan gavgavim uan navibar an…®ng…®va aghumra ik…®va egh os…®mt…®zir ia bativim ater. Ia fo, Ekiam Izamin Dughiam a bar rogh…®ra ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia tuivigh gavgavigh ik…®.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt 1 Korin 4:5; Jems 4:11\x*Nan adarasi, ia God…®n gumazamizir igharazibar atar…®va ak…®ribar me m…®k…®man mark…®. Ia fo, ia kamagh…®n damut…®, God jas…®n m…®n otogh ian arazir kuraba tuis…®gham. Ia oragh, jas…®n kam a tiar akam…®n tughav iti!  
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt Matyu 5:12; Hibru 11:32-38\x*Nan adarasi, ia fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir Ekiam…®n ziam…®n akam akuniziba, ia me g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Apaniba arazir kurabar me gami, ez…® me tuivigha gavgavigha os…®mt…®zir kam ateri. Ia men arazir kam inigh, egh men g…®n mang…®.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:6; Jop 1:21-22; 2:10; 42:10; Onger Akaba 103:8; 111:4; Matyu 5:10-11\x*Ia oragh. E ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazamizir tuivigha gavgavigha os…®mt…®ziba ateriba, me bar akuegha derav…®ra iti.‚Äù Ia Jop…®n eghaghanim g…®fo, a tugha gavgavigha os…®mt…®zir a batoziba a bar da ateri. Ez…® ia fo, Ekiam g…®n bar arazir aghuim…®n a gami. E bar fo, Ekiam en apangkuvav…®ra iti, egha zurara bar derav…®ra e gami. 
\s1 E guizbang…®ra p…®n dar…®gh m…®k…®man kogham 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt Matyu 5:34-37\x*Nan adarasi, e damuamin bizir faragha zuim, a kamak…®n. Dughiar ia akar d…®k…®r…®zim damuamim, ia pura God…®n Nguibam…®n ziam d…®ponan mark…®, egh guizbang…®ra dar…®gh nguazim o bizir igharazim d…®ponan mark…®. Egh ia suam, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra bizir kam damuam.‚Äù Egh ia suam, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra bizir kam damuan kogham.‚Äù Egh ia uan akam…®n g…®n mang…®. Ia m…®k…®m guizbang…®ra p…®n d…®boroght…®, God ivezir kuram ia danigham. 
\s1 God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumaziba, me God ko m…®gei, men azangs…®ziba bar gavgavir ekiam iti 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 5:13 \xt Efesus 5:19; Kolosi 3:16\x*Ez…® ian tav ti os…®mt…®zim ateri? Kamagh…®n a God ko m…®k…®m. Ez…® ian tav ti bar akonge? An Ekiam…®n ziam fer ighiabar amu.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Mak 6:13; 16:18\x*Ez…® ian tav ti arei? A Krais…®n adarazir gumazamizir dapanibar diaght…®, me iz…® a bagh God ko m…®k…®m…®va, Ekiam…®n ziam…®n borem an m…®karzim daghuigh.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 5:15 \xt Aisaia 33:24; Matyu 9:2; Mak 16:18\x*Egh me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…® God ko m…®k…®mt…®, azangs…®zir kaba an akurvagh a damight…®ma, a ghuamaghegham. Ekiam ar…®mariar gumazir kam uam a fegham. Eght…® an amizir arazir kuraba, Ekiam da g…®n amadagham.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 5:16 \xt God…®n Araziba 9:18-20; 1 Samuel 12:18; 1 Atriviba 13:6; Onger Akaba 34:15; Jon 9:31\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia vaghvagh uan arazir kurabar gun God…®n gumazamizir igharazibav k…®m. Eght…® God ian akurvaghs…®, ia uari bagh God ko m…®k…®mt…®, God ia damight…® ia ua deragham. Ez…® gumazim o amizir God…®n damazim…®n deraghav…®ra itim God ko m…®gei, an azangs…®zim bar gavgavir ekiam iti, eght…® a igharaz darazir akurvagham. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt 1 Atriviba 17:1; 18:1; Luk 4:25; Aposel 14:15\x*Elaija, e nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamizibar m…®n garir gumazim. Egha a pamtem God ko m…®kemegha ghaze, amozim izan kogham. Ez…® God amozim…®n t…®vaz…®ma amozim azenir 3pla ko iak…®nir 6plan nguazim…®n izezir puvat…®.\f + \fr 5:17 \ft Elaija, a fom…®ra itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim.\f* 
\v 18 \x - \xo 5:18 \xt 1 Atriviba 18:42-45\x*Egha a g…®n ua God ko m…®geima, God amozim amadaz…®ma a izaghir…®, ez…® dagheba uam azenibar aghui. 
\s1 Gumazamiziba guiz…®n tuavim ateght…®, e ua me inigh izam 
\p  
\v 19-20 \x - \xo 5:19-20 \xt Onger Akaba 51:13; Aghuzir Akaba 10:12; Matyu 18:15; Rom 11:14; 1 Korin 9:22; Galesia 6:1; 1 Timoti 4:16; 1 Pita 4:8\x*Nan adarasi, ian tav guiz…®n akam…®n tuavim ategh pura akar igharazim…®n g…®n mangam, eght…® ian tav uam a inigh iz…® guiz…®n akam…®n tuavim dat…®gham, kar arazir bar aghuim. Ia akar kam deragh a g…®n…®ghn…®gh! Ian tav gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amibar akuraght…®ma me tuavir kuram ategh ua God bagh izegham, an arazir kurabagh amir gumazamizir kabar duabar akuraght…®ma me oveghan kogham. Eght…® arazir kamra God arazir kurar av…®riba g…®n amadagham.\f + \fr 5:19-20 \ft Marazi ghaze, Krais…®n g…®n zuir darasi, men marazi God…®n guiz…®n akam ataki. Ez…® Jems men arazibar k…®rasa, ak…®nafarir kam osiri.\f*